{"tid":2057961,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中國駐英大使劉曉明：希望英國商界能夠客觀看待國安法立法","createTime":"2020-06-09T19:24:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T22:46:09.000Z","uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"bede30b6a7da3f3903e49caff064805d6bfbef56","tid":2057961,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T19:24:40.000Z","msg":"A prosperous &amp; stable Hong Kong is in the interests of both China&amp;UK. <br />\n<br />\nI hope UK business community will view the national security legislation for HKSAR from an objective and reasonable perspective, &amp; contribute positive energy to HK&rsquo;s long-term prosperity and stability.<br />\n<br />\n繁榮且穩定的香港符合中英兩國的利益。我希望英國商界能夠客觀地看待香港的國安法，這是為了香港的長遠繁榮與穩定作出的立法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ambliuxiaoming/status/1270433016507174913\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fambliuxiaoming%2Fstatus%2F1270433016507174913&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XelrTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=009b9f72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fambliuxiaoming%2Fstatus%2F1270433016507174913&h=f30587fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ambliuxiaoming/status/1270433016507174913</a>"},{"pid":"0b03d001a1b214aa2b29b5764a29b440d9a4c136","tid":2057961,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T19:26:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b27b9aaa7bca0f24728d665deb25964e6b65a95f","tid":2057961,"uid":92188,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T19:27:34.000Z","msg":"英國唔好淆<br />\n最客觀嘅睇法就係破壞中英聯合聲明囉"},{"pid":"b6a75da9168707f23ffee6b29659fe30fbbd5587","tid":2057961,"uid":106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T19:27:51.000Z","msg":"唔好縮！"},{"pid":"2afff45a4cb74a484d353b9f91963db534cb6d51","tid":2057961,"uid":143343,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T19:2